#compdef harmonia
# ============================================================================
# _harmonia — zsh completion for **harmonia** — RobertBendun/harmonia,
#              the **synchronized sequencer + player for laptop
#              orchestra** that lets a distributed ensemble of
#              musicians (each at their own laptop, connected over a
#              local network) trigger MIDI files / live algorithmic
#              music / pre-recorded audio in beat-locked synchrony
#              via the **Ableton Link** protocol.  Built by Robert
#              Bendun of the Polish-language **laptop orchestra
#              tradition** (Akademia Sztuki w Szczecinie / Akademia
#              Muzyczna im. Karola Lipińskiego we Wrocławiu).
#              Embeds a browser-renderable UI (axum + htmx + maud
#              templating) so each performer drives the local
#              instance via `localhost:8080` while Ableton Link
#              synchronizes the beat phase + tempo across the
#              entire LAN.  Rust=175 OPENING leg of new Axis 120
#              (MIDI / IEEE 1639 + ALSA / CoreMIDI / WinMM
#              cross-platform MIDI I/O) via the canonical Rust
#              MIDI library **midir** (Boddlnagg/midir, the
#              de-facto Rust MIDI dependency).
# ============================================================================
#
# UPSTREAM
